---
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import Kicker from '../Kicker.astro';
import TentMotif from '../TentMotif.astro';
import storyImage from '../../assets/hero/hero-mt-kenya.jpg';
---
<section id="story" class="relative bg-cream py-28 md:py-44">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-wide px-6 md:px-10">
    <div class="grid gap-16 md:gap-24 md:grid-cols-12 items-start">
      <div class="md:col-span-5">
        <div class="reveal reveal--fade-up"><Kicker tone="coffee">Our Story</Kicker></div>
        <h2 class="reveal reveal--fade-up mt-7 font-display text-display-lg text-forest text-balance" style="--reveal-delay:100ms;">
          Born from a love of the open road, the mountain, and the morning light.
        </h2>
        <div class="reveal reveal--fade mt-10 flex items-center gap-4" style="--reveal-delay:200ms;">
          <TentMotif size={48} tone="coffee" />
          <span class="hairline flex-1"></span>
        </div>
        <div class="reveal reveal--scale-image mt-10 relative overflow-hidden aspect-[5/6]" style="--reveal-delay:200ms;">
          <Image
            src={storyImage}
            alt="Mtalii tented camp glowing at golden hour beneath Mount Kenya"
            widths={[480, 720, 960, 1280]}
            sizes="(min-width:768px) 40vw, 100vw"
            quality={82}
            format="webp"
            loading="lazy"
            class="absolute inset-0 h-full w-full object-cover"
          />
          <span class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-ink/20 via-transparent to-transparent"></span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="md:col-span-6 md:col-start-7 prose-editorial md:pt-24">
        <div class="reveal reveal--fade-up" style="--reveal-delay:150ms;">
          <p>
            Mtalii Bush Camps began with a shared vision of adventure. Inspired by a love for the
            open road, our founders journeyed to Nanyuki in a 4x4, seeking the freedom of the
            mountains. They were immediately captivated by the crisp air and the majestic presence
            of Mount Kenya.
          </p>
          <p>
            What started as a personal retreat evolved into a mission to share this magic with the
            world. Today, Mtalii Bush Camps is where adventure meets comfort &mdash; whether
            you&rsquo;re here for a challenging climb, a corporate retreat, or a peaceful escape,
            we invite you to start your next unforgettable chapter with us.
          </p>
        </div>
        <span class="reveal reveal--fade hairline block w-full mt-10" style="--reveal-delay:300ms;"></span>
        <p class="reveal reveal--fade-up mt-10 font-display italic text-2xl md:text-3xl text-coffee leading-snug text-balance" style="--reveal-delay:400ms;">
          &ldquo;Strangers become friends &mdash; around the same fire, beneath the same
          mountain.&rdquo;
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
